{"tid":1798893,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"停止裝修藍店？","createTime":"2019-12-26T14:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T16:40:34.000Z","uid":57221,"like":6,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3e98added607941ba9684d5026120d0b863fd1b5","tid":1798893,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:29:35.000Z","msg":"呢個垃圾post咁撚多<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大愛撚</span></span></strong>話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>要觀察下 要原諒</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">下次間藍店害死埋手足<br />\n上fb打兩隻字話轉黃就可以冇事㗎啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>反正你地又唔洗問下比間藍店害死嘅手足</strong></span><br />\n自己可以決定可以原諒班垃圾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且口講觀察<br />\n過一排你班垃圾咪又係冇左件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑撚死人咩  監察<br />\n<strong>兩日唔記得左啦</strong><br />\n<br />\n無法想像過左成六個月<br />\n仍然有呢啲垃圾心態<br />\n<br />\n大門橫丁真係好驚比人裝修喎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1798769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1798769</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6b2e5bfdee03e42527f4381f2f500a0af89f5ca8","tid":1798893,"uid":57221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:30:47.000Z","msg":"sorry呀害到你啲手足被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我轉黃㗎啦<br />\n原諒我ok？"},{"pid":"3ee1ad1c716cb4917896d938502b1612ffeee544","tid":1798893,"uid":29823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"要去你自己去 我唔割<br />\n只係仲有更加多仆街嘅鋪頭 比佢更值得執笠先"},{"pid":"c9828bb32c5b2eb8e44b3aa79a354c1d0b456d7f","tid":1798893,"uid":57221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ee1ad1c716cb4917896d938502b1612ffeee544","tid":1798893,"uid":29823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:31:42.000Z","msg":"要去你自己去 我唔割<br />\n只係仲有更加多仆